      <p>You can host <strong><%= @venue.capacity %> friends! </strong></p>
      <p><strong>Our best price for you:</strong> <%= sprintf('%.2f', @venue.price) %> â‚¬</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
      <p> Here could be a map </p>
    </div>
    <p>Contact information:</p>
    <p><%= @venue.user.email %></p>
